com.flowpowered.commons.concurrent.set

Class TSyncIntHashSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flowpowered.commons.concurrent.set.TSyncIntHashSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    gnu.trove.set.TIntSet, gnu.trove.TIntCollection

    public class TSyncIntHashSet
extends Object
implements gnu.trove.set.TIntSet
    This is a synchronised version of the Trove IntHashSet. Read/write locks are used to synchronise access. By default, it creates 16 sub-maps and there is a separate read/write lock for each submap.
